The US: Repetition is the mother of wisdom
It is almost funny, with Barack Obama, the president with a reputation as the smartest, repeated in the strategy of his predecessor, whom he considered it nejhloupějšího.
When he finally vypotil his eagerly awaited Afghan doctrine, it turned out that it copied over kopírák of Bush's Iraq three years ago.
Not only in the text itself uses the word several times turnover as in Iraq ", but did not hesitate even to use the name of Bush's declaration in January 2007 as the name of their own declaration: " the new way forward ".
Three years ago, However, he criticized Bush's idea to send fresh military reinforcements to Iraq, beset by civil war as " irresponsible and disastrous consequences of their decision ".
The subsequent months have shown, however, that Bush's strategy based on the advice of field commanders was the only possible and veleúspěšnou so today in the intelligence about Iraq at all levels from talking.
Bush's reputation, but he left to his successor, a much more grateful starting point than expected.
In Afghanistan, Barack Obama in hopes that a miracle again.
The increase in military contingent asked him again a field commanders, in particular the top commander of the Afghan operation, General Stanley McCristal, which even despite subordinačním harshly criticized the practice hesitant shooter in the White House.
He asked 40 thousand men, in order to break the situation for the better.
The president of the three months he hesitated, but nothing better, and so at least 10 thousand soldiers.
In fact, Europe was able to squeeze out the promise of a further 5 thousands, even though he initially counted at least 10.
Most problematic for Obama's strategy appears to be to his intention to begin the withdrawal of troops from Afghanistan for 18 months and stop this process within three years. of the Obama doctrine raises more questions than it provides answers.
Many doubt that the increase in half - baked fruit gives the same procedure as in Iraq.
Despite the internecine wars of recent years is the Iraqi society relatively well organized, its leaders to honor the agreement.
The Afghan situation is characterised by the opposite sign - the one shall not count and no agreements have not been honored.
Wrong, under these conditions, the Afghan security forces used as day to day depending on the Lord, as it suits them.
Political institutions, even if they are formally established, will remain just a Potemkin village, for which they will continue to fester patriarchal tribal relations.
The balance of interests of the various ethnic groups is extremely difficult due to clutter ratios, which further complicate the Pakistani and Iranian influences.
Neither the establishment of a " akceschopného state ", which is a minimalist objective of the operation, it does not look too real.
The time of Obama's strategy strikes his voluntarism.
For the past eight years, the situation has only worsened in Afghanistan and is now on the verge of explosion.
Believe in that sending soldiers into a war in order to " return home early ' cause there made a miracle, can only really romantic soul, the facts.
From a political point of view, is to set a date for withdrawal of troops by the Taliban, because it would be seen as an implicit declaration of American defeat.
The last NATO summit showed that the Europeans ' willingness to participate in combat operations in Afghanistan is nearing.
European politicians can not and do not want to explain to voters how the safety of Germany or Italy is linked to the war in the foothills of the Hindu Kush.
Another factor capable of radically to intervene in the situation is developments around Iran.
If the situation continues to deteriorate and intensified sanctions on the Iranians do not do, there will be before the United States, the question of whether to try to solve the problem of the use of military force.
Answer it will be just the time when, according to Obama, America will proceed to the withdrawal from Afghanistan.
Any such solution, however, will mean a dramatic turnaround in the Afghan situation.
The only for Barack Obama, is the fact that the presidential election three years left, and so there's still plenty of time to come up with another strategy, if this proves to be a total flop.
