Hyundai comply with the unions will cancel all overtime.
Management Nosovice Hyundai car with the unions agreed to cancel all of overtime.
It is because of the often nařizovaným overtime on Monday announced a union strike emergency.
Confirmed car Hyundai spokesman Petr Vanek.
Management, however, wants to trade union leaders to agree even on a Saturday this year's shift.
We can not waver in our production schedule, that it is essential, therefore, was designed to be voluntary overtime on Saturday, 19 December, with the result that would have made the two shifts, he said.
Server Sedmička. cz wrote that the company employees who work the Saturday shift, offered a bonus of 400.
He will get people back to work Saturday, 28 November.
The company, according to Vanek decided to change the way to motivate employees in the proposed overtime.
Either you leave to pay extra for overtime or compensatory time off may choose 28th December, and thus about the day to extend the Christmas holidays, said Vaněk.
In addition, all employees get paid for Saturday shifts and lunch fare.
Given that overtime was nejurgentnějším and most distressing point in terms of comments and complaints from trade unionists, protesters and employees last week spontaneously stopped production, the lead yesterday afternoon, decided with immediate effect the abolition of overtime for the month of December, he said.
Staff car until last week were forced to practice every day to work after an eight - hour shift, even two - hour overtime.
After the signing of the agreement, the union strike emergency recall
Further negotiations between the management and the union is to take place on Friday morning.
The union chief Peter Cook on Wednesday said that if they agree to meet the requirements and sign a joint document to be ready the strike call.
The situation in the car came to a head last week on Wednesday, when about 400 employees because of the constant overtime.
Also protested against poor pay conditions and alleged bullying.
Management opposed to overtime, workers must do to satisfy the requirements for the supply of cars.
Unionists in their call strike notice on Monday also demanded that the sanctions are not sanctioned by any employees who last Wednesday cut production.
In the field of trade unions after the company required in order to stem the overtime work to a minimum.
In addition to her wish this year to pay the salaries of 5000 crowns.
Nosovice carmaker Hyundai, which currently employs 2,000 people.
Series production company rode last November.
In September this year produced about 80,000 cars, its current production capacity of 200,000 cars per year.
Czech discovery: a substance that takes on ' hardy ' HIV virus
A team of Czech and German researchers testing new compounds that can slow the spread of HIV in the body.
The main advantage of improved compounds is that it takes to viruses that have acquired immunity against drugs.
This fact, in some cases outweigh the fact that the compound is a normal variant of " not so strongly as some already available medicines.
AIDS can not yet be cured.
However, patients can greatly extend the life of a combination of drugs that inhibit the reproduction of HIV in the body.
Their use, however, is accompanied by a number of side effects.
Partial suppression of propagation of the virus has also resulted in the development of the so - called resistant viruses against which the drugs are ineffective.
The work of the experts from The three institutions of the Academy of Sciences, of the Institute of Chemical Technology in Prague and the University of Heidelberg opens the way to deal with the resistance to the virus.
Have shown that a substance called metalokarborany work on a protein responsible for the reproduction of HIV.
Metalokarborany are compounds of boron, carbon and hydrogen, and cobalt.
These compounds are blocking the spread of the virus than any other currently used drugs, and therefore may overcome the problem of resistance.
In his work, scientists have come with the new ' improved ' compounds prepared on the basis of knowledge of the molecular mechanism of their ties to the viral proteins.
Metalokarborany a unique three - dimensional structure: two mnohostěnné cage consisting of atoms of boron, hydrogen and carbon atom are linked by a metal, in this case.
Treacherous and resistant virus
HIV protease is a protein of the HIV, which is necessary for the life cycle of the virus.
Without HIV protease cleavage caused by the HIV virus would not have been mature infectious viral particles.
When we stop HIV protease, and stop the spread of the virus in the patient's body, the scientists explain in a press release issued by the Institute of organic chemistry and biochemistry of the Academy of Sciences of the Czech Republic.
In the work published in the scientific journal, the Journal of Medicinal Chemistry scientists describe a series of compounds in which two pairs of cages (see table) are linked by a short organic chain, which is systematically.
A little weaker, but more reliable
The effect of this series of anti - HIV protease was tested in vitro and also against the resistant (resistant) variants derived from patients infected with HIV.
The effect of the metalokarboranů a normal variant of the enzyme is not as strong as clinically used drugs, but does not lose its effect on drug - resistant variants against which are used drugs are often ineffective.
The unique mechanism of action and as well as its other properties such as biological and chemical stability, low toxicity and the possibility of further chemical modifications of metalokarboranů is interesting compounds for further research towards the design of effective drugs against HIV, says Pavlina Řezáčová, head of the lab Structural Biology Institute of organic chemistry and biochemistry and Institute of molecular genetics, of the Academy of Sciences.
