Managerial revolution or the end of the economic intelligence?
If nothing changes in the management of large French companies, our fight for the development of the economic intelligence was unnecessary.
For more than ten years, is reminiscent of the behaviour of the managers of large companies employees access to business - to - consumer marketing before revolution: the point is to co - identify themselves with the " values " means identified from the mountain, as it was before, when it was necessary to impose on the consumer products which have emerged heads of the ideas factory technicians.
The fact that the customer has become a centre of entrepreneurial companies marketing strategy, the conquest of the market in the right direction ... even if the authoritarian efforts to impose on the products different from customer preferences, returning regularly!
Passive attitude of the staff can lead to death.
Suicide in companies France Telecom, PSA and Renault are just the visible part of a much more general phenomenon, which affects mostly managerial cadres.
The demobilization adversely affects the development of all intellectual functions of the company, including research and development, and, more importantly, economic intelligence.
And, indeed, EI " requires all interested parties (...) active approach and the ability to predict " and requires from employees who are completely at odds with the authoritarian revenue management.
Therefore, we call on the managerial revolution, which should aim to bring the staff at the center of the interests of the company as well as a client.
The relative The usefulness of internal polls.
Internal polls - as the questionnaire submitted by the employees of the company Orange - will contribute to the revolution in management practices?
Unfortunately, I'm afraid not.
Mainly because I was convinced that, in the face of the new situation, of the structure of the different turns back give priority to this ... you do what I always do!
Furthermore, because that authoritarianism, as one of the pathology of power, with the severity of their own failures.
And finally, because most of the executives have a simplified view of human behavior.
Because they are graduates of engineers have a mechanical interpretation of psychology.
For the sake of convenience of thought are acquired by the old theory, currently again " from the US and re - animated " in the U. S. knowledge of the scientific institutes and the media.
In fact, it is possible to move the " levers " (sic) the involvement of managers, showed a recent survey of the Agency Ipsos Figaro. fr site, which only strengthens the management personnel in the position of a mechanical procedure, unfit for today's world.
To identify and measure the factors mobilization.
On the contrary, the revolution is necessary for the proper functioning of modern enterprises, provides for the adoption of the definitive vision of human behavior.
Lies in the integration of the basic insight into all the projects and practice management: for the employees of the commitments to the company will be possible only if they seem clear means to achieve their dreams, ambitions and projects.
Currently, this concept of the motivation of staff involved in the study only motivation functional analysis.
These studies have shown that their businesses on the basis of predetermined doxy, which will allow them to use through the image, which the company says, look at what to them to realize their life goals.
Thanks to the identification and measurement of these factors, managers can mobilize to control, predict and pre - empted on their " social power ", and its management of human resources " on the right path ".
This creates a breeding ground for the development of a sound and effective economic intelligence.
