New instruments for valuing cars
In these days of storms and accidents, not only make car services.
Every day thousands of cars, which are suffering towed to a service where the expert must assess the damage and the cost of the repair.
No event is not the same and the calculation of the cost of the parts and labor of the time can be long and difficult work.
Calculate the cost of the repairs from 20,000 to 30,000 euros, including parts and labor, it may take two or three hours.
However, with the support of the new computer tools, it would be a matter of minutes.
Therefore, almost 100% of the experts used this type of system.
Suppliers of services and solutions for the estimation of claims and maintenance services to the harvesting of information provided to them by the producers to establish and then to offer their customers a useful tool.
In Spain, a group of American Solera is the leading company, 80% of the evaluation is carried out with its products.
Other companies that compete in the field of measurement instruments and the development of information on the sector, and are GtMotive Eurotax.
Work with the data provided by the manufacturer, is not simple.
According to Edward Velazquez, director of the business Audatex, working in Spain, with 63 producers and importers, and each of them gives them the information in a different format.
In addition, the amount of data processing is still growing, as in the past five years has been mentioned several versions, variants and motor solution than in the previous 15 years.
As soon as the new vehicle will enter the market, these enterprises will work.
It is a very real work, because it is necessary to each of the thousands of parts of the vehicle and to determine its value.
In addition, for each model is carried out " intelligent " the processing ", where it is possible to " various parts of tourist cars.
As for the model with massive sales, the work can be done in a week, if the process is very fast.
As regards the minor car, it may take three or four months. At present, Audatex has complete information on 99.2% of the cars sold in Spain.
Among the most exclusive models, which have information, Porsche, but, for example, not a Ferrari or Lamborghini.
Concerning mobile park in circulation exceed 99%.
To perform the work documenting and developing databases Audatex has eight centers located around the world (Spain, France, Germany, the US, Brazil, Mexico, China, and Japan) , and each of them specializes in a particular brand.
The national headquarters is in Alcobendas (Madrid) .
There is more than a hundred engineers (normally experts in mechanics) works at the same time, with three computer screens.
Audatex invests 90 million euros a year to the development of these databases.
Each month, included 2.5 million customers receive information and updates every two days.
The processing of this stream of information allows enterprises to different uses, and the provision of various products.
The most common use is focus on repair and maintenance, but in each country there are also tools for the management of spare parts or for the calculation of the sales or the residual value of a car.
The firm, which is available in the guide, which shall inform the value of used cars in Spain, is Eurotax.
Audatex is in our country offers, but in the United States, yes.
With regard to the products, which offers Audatex, it is easy to get the support that can be used by professionals in the sector.
The firm offers ten různýchnástrojů, while the star product is the AudaPlus, standard solutions to the valuation of claims for an expert.
Includes cars, motorcycles and light and heavy industrial vehicles.
In addition to the cost of the parts, also includes the time to correct the estimated by the manufacturer or lakovnou.
This instrument shall be paid according to use for each evaluation.
The highest price is 5.75 euros for customers who use it, a little more than ten times in a month.
Then any undertaking which carries out one thousands of estimates, negotiate a price with Audatex.
Other products such as AudaVIN allow full identification of vehicles and equipment, with which came off the assembly line, only on the basis of the first number.
AudaGlass focus on glass AudaSubastas vehicles and is open to the professional services sector on the Internet, which allows the vehicle to surrender to the total outstanding event.
The statistical service is very useful for the identification of trend analysis or design geodemografických deviations are found by the brands or models.
For example, it is possible to study how much the brand has undergone modelůurčité service due to accident or how many suffered serious claims for a certain period of time.
GT Motive is the only the Spanish company, which is dedicated to the development of this type of instruments.
Among other things, sells Gt Estimate, which is also intended for experts, as well as providing digital images, access to works or those of the manufacturer and the official times.
GT Motive is a group company based in 1971 as a supplier of services and solutions to assess the damage, accidents or maintenance of cars
GT Guía valuation of its historical reference product on the market.
They work with 24,000 users in garages 3.100 experts and 53 of the insurance companies.
The volume of sales increased by 20% a year for the last three years and in 2008 charged by 10.8 million.
At the beginning of last year, began the process of internationalisation of the installation of the office in Paris.
Audatex originated in Germany in 1966 and in 1979 became established in Spain.
According to the company sources of 62% of her brother is produced in Europe and 38% in North and South America. works with 900 insurance companies and 33,000 services, of which 3,000 in Spain.
