This platform was founded in 1996 in Germany and manages more than 650,000 operations across Europe, including 500,000 in Germany.
Among the major markets, with Spain, Greece, Poland and Turkey.
The site currently has more than 1,500 registered vendors and 4,000 experts.
Manages 3,000 daily ads and on the Spanish market has added about 100 new homes every day.
