The budget of the service in four steps
With the tool - taller firm guarantees that the user gets the budget only in four steps: identification of the vehicle, finding a replacement part, the budget is the creation of a budget.
Ease of use is an essential condition for these systems, in particular for the belief in a higher age professionals who, to a greater or lesser extent, are restrained in the use of new management techniques.
The database contains 1034 vehicles, including tourist 666, 109 field, 137, 78 trucks and 44 delivery.
Naturally, it is necessary to use a computer with an Internet connection.
After the identification of the model, which is to be by using the chassis number, appears realistic graphical representation of the model and then select the required a spare part.
The user can include variables such as the price of labor, overtime or discounts, and then print out and passed on to the customer.
